text: Ahmed Ouyahia (born July 2, 1952) is an Algerian politician. He was the Prime Minister of Algeria from August 16, 2017 to March 12, 2019. Ouyahia was already Prime Minister from 1995 to 1998, from 2003 to 2006, and from 2008 to 2012."Bio express : Ahmed Ouyahia", Jeune Afrique, 9 June 2009 . He was also Minister of Justice for a time. He formed and was president of the RND party. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Algeria
